content.rendered: A fumigation certificate, sometimes referred to as a pest-control certificate, is a document that serves as confirmation that any wooden packing materials (ie, pallets) used in a cargo shipment have been fumigated. Pest Control company need to provide certificate and keep data of certificates. Our application help to maintain these certificate online with multiple users. For more details call Mob No. 7030314949
